    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical stewardship and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a refined driving experience that balances performance with long-term reliability. Every component has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for operational excellence and safety.",
