    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride and it's looking for a brand new home. It\u2019s been super well-maintained and is in really solid shape, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs like a dream and has plenty of life left in it! Honestly, I'm going to miss this one, but I'm excited for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is excellent, with the critical subframe reinforcement already completed and a cooling system overhaul recently performed. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression across all six cylinders and rod bearing tolerances\u2014remain within tight factory specifications. This is a visceral, analog machine optimized for turn-in response and high-RPM performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
